    s390-ccw: Fix alignment for CCW1
    
    The commit 198c0d1f9df8c4 s390x/css: check ccw address validity
    exposes an alignment issue in ccw bios.
    
    According to PoP the CCW must be doubleword aligned. Let's fix
    this in the bios.
    
